<div class="container">
    <section class="section">
        <h2>Our History</h2>
        <p>Founded in 1911 by the De La Salle Brothers, De La Salle University (DLSU) is one of the Philippines' leading institutions of higher learning, known for its academic excellence, research innovation, and commitment to social transformation.

            Originally established as De La Salle College in Paco, Manila, the school moved to Taft Avenue, Manila in 1921. Throughout its history, DLSU has played a significant role in shaping leaders in business, engineering, science, technology, education, and the humanities.

            Despite the devastation of World War II, during which 16 La Salle Brothers and 25 civilians tragically lost their lives, the university persevered, rebuilding itself into a center for quality Catholic education. In 1975, it officially became De La Salle University, offering a wide range of undergraduate and graduate programs.

            Today, DLSU is recognized as a premier research institution and a Center of Excellence in multiple disciplines. It is a member of the ASEAN University Network (AUN) and continues to uphold its Lasallian mission of faith, service, and communion, empowering students to become future leaders and changemakers.

            .</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section" style="background: #f1f1f1; padding: 40px; border-radius: 10px;">
        <h2>Mission & Vision</h2>
        <p><strong>Mission:</strong> DLSU is dedicated to providing a transformative education that integrates faith, service, and knowledge.</p>
        <p><strong>Vision:</strong> To be a globally recognized institution that fosters innovation, sustainability, and human development.</p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
        <h2>Lasallian Values</h2>
        <p>DLSU upholds the core values of Faith, Zeal for Service, and Communion in Mission. These principles guide the university in shaping students into responsible and compassionate leaders.</p>
    </section>
